remarks.para:
This member is deprecated. Whether the key is bound to the secure hardware is known only
            once the key has been imported. To find out, use:
            <pre>PrivateKey key = ...; // private key from KeyChain

            KeyFactory keyFactory =
                KeyFactory.getInstance(key.getAlgorithm(), "AndroidKeyStore");
            KeyInfo keyInfo = keyFactory.getKeySpec(key, KeyInfo.class);
            if (keyInfo.isInsideSecureHardware()) {
                // The key is bound to the secure hardware of this Android}</pre>
